Title: A note on Polyakov's nonlocal form of the effective action

Authors: J.S.Dowker

Comments: 4 pages, Plain TeX,MUTP/93/22

Journal-ref: Class. Quant. Grav. 11 (1994) L7

A technical point regarding the invariance of Polyakov's nonlocal form of theeffective action under uniform rescalings is briefly addressed.